#, no-wrap
msgid "[[!meta title=\"French journal Mediapart supports Tails, others should too\"]]\n"
msgstr "[[!meta title=\"La revista francesa Mediapart dona suport a Tails, d'altres també ho haurien de fer\"]]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "[[!tag announce]]\n"
msgstr "[[!tag announce]]\n"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"We are very excited to announce that [Mediapart](https://www.mediapart.fr), "
"an independent French investigative journal, has decided to support Tails "
"financially every year."
msgstr ""
"Estem molt emocionats d'anunciar que [Mediapart](https://www.mediapart.fr), "
"una revista d'investigació independent francesa, ha decidit donar suport "
"econòmic a Tails cada any."

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "[[!img mediapart.png link=\"no\"]]\n"
msgstr "[[!img mediapart.png link=\"no\"]]\n"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"In the past years, Mediapart has played a central role in the revelation and "
"investigation of several major French political scandals. As such they are "
"well aware of the digital threats faced by their sources, their journalists, "
"and their readers."
msgstr ""
"En els últims anys, Mediapart ha tingut un paper central en la revelació i "
"investigació de diversos escàndols polítics francesos importants. Com a "
"tals, són molt conscients de les amenaces digitals a les quals s'enfronten "
"les seves fonts, els seus periodistes i els seus lectors."

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"Tails has gained recognition by being used by Edward Snowden and the "
"journalists reporting on his NSA leaks in 2014. [According to Barton Gellman]"
"(https://pressfreedomfoundation.org/blog/2014/04/help-support-little-known-"
"privacy-tool-has-been-critical-journalists-reporting-nsa):"
msgstr ""
"Tails ha guanyat reconeixement en ser utilitzat per Edward Snowden i els "
"periodistes que van informar sobre les seves filtracions de la NSA el 2014. "
"[Segons Barton Gellman](https://pressfreedomfoundation.org/blog/2014/04/help-"
"support-little-known-privacy-tool-has-been-critical-journalists-reporting-"
"nsa):"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"« *Privacy and encryption work, but it's too easy to make a mistake that "
"exposes you. Tails puts the essential tools in one place, with a design that "
"makes it hard to screw them up. I could not have talked to Edward Snowden "
"without this kind of protection. I wish I'd had it years ago.* »"
msgstr ""
"«*La privadesa i l'encriptatge funcionen, però és massa fàcil cometre un "
"error que us exposa. Tails posa les eines essencials en un sol lloc, amb un "
"disseny que dificulta fer les coses malament. No hauria pogut parlar amb "
"Edward Snowden sense aquest tipus de protecció. Tant de bo hagués tingut "
"Tails fa anys.*»"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"Since then [[many journalists around the world|news/"
"who_are_you_helping#journalists]] understood this approach and adopted Tails "
"to make it easier to stay safe. As Jean-Marc Manach puts it:"
msgstr ""
"Des d'aleshores, [[molts periodistes d'arreu del món|news/"
"who_are_you_helping#journalists]] van entendre aquest enfocament i van "
"adoptar Tails per facilitar-se la seguretat. Com diu Jean-Marc Manach:"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"« *War reporters have to buy helmets, bullet-proof vests and rent armored "
"cars; journalists using the Internet for their investigations are much "
"luckier: to be as secured as war reporters, they only have to download "
"Tails, burn it on a CD, install it on a SD card, and learn the basics of "
"information and communication security, and it's free!* »"
msgstr ""
"«*Els periodistes de guerra han de comprar cascs, armilles antibales i "
"llogar cotxes blindats; els periodistes que utilitzen Internet per a les "
"seves investigacions són molt més afortunats: per estar tan segurs com els "
"periodistes de guerra, només han de baixar Tails, gravar-lo en un CD, "
"instal·lar-lo en una targeta SD i aprendre els conceptes bàsics de seguretat "
"de la informació i la comunicació, i és gratis!*»"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"In the same way that news organizations invest in physical security or "
"proprietary software tools to do their work, news organizations should also "
"invest in free software tools that, as security experts like Bruce Schneier "
"have repeatedly stated, are going to be safe:"
msgstr ""
"De la mateixa manera que les organitzacions de premsa inverteixen en "
"seguretat física o eines de programari privatiu per fer la seva feina, les "
"mateixes organitzacions haurien d'invertir en eines de programari lliure "
"que, segons experts en seguretat com Bruce Schneier han afirmat "
"repetidament, seran segures:"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"« *I think most of the public domain privacy tools are going to be safe, "
"yes. [...] I think that Tails is going to be safe. [...] You know, the NSA "
"has a big lever when a tool is written closed-source by a for-profit "
"corporation. There are levers they have that they don't have in the open "
"source international, altruistic community. And these are generally written "
"by crypto-paranoids, they're pretty well designed.* »"
msgstr ""
"«*Crec que la majoria de les eines de privadesa de domini públic seran "
"segures, sí. […] Crec que Tails estarà segur. […] Ja sabeu, la NSA té una "
"gran palanca quan una corporació amb ànim de lucre escriu una eina en codi "
"tancat. Hi ha palanques de la NSA que no tenen a la comunitat altruista "
"internacional de codi obert. I aquests són generalment escrits per cripto-"
"paranoides, estan bastant ben dissenyats.*»"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"As such, Tails has been the recommended secure platform for use with the "
"[SecureDrop](https://securedrop.org/) and [GlobaLeaks](https://globaleaks."
"org/) whistle-blowing platforms."
msgstr ""
"Com a tal, Tails ha estat la plataforma segura recomanada per ser utilitzada "
"amb les plataformes de denúncia [SecureDrop](https://securedrop.org/) i "
"[GlobaLeaks](https://globaleaks.org/)."

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"Talking about the challenges of the adoption of encryption by journalists, "
"the Internet freedom expert [Christopher Soghoian said at #EncryptNews]"
"(https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JktB6h-qnKA), a conference on digital "
"security and journalism:"
msgstr ""
"Parlant sobre els reptes de l'adopció de l'encriptatge per part dels "
"periodistes, l'expert en llibertat d'Internet [Christopher Soghoian va dir a "
"#EncryptNews](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JktB6h-qnKA), una conferència "
"sobre seguretat digital i periodisme:"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"« *News organizations need to also contribute to this community pool of "
"tools. We need to have [reporters] contributing patches to PGP, OTR, and "
"Tails. These organizations need to be funding $5.000 or $10.000 improvements "
"to make these tools better. Because everyone is relying on these tools and "
"none of the major organizations that are actually benefiting them are "
"actually contributing to their development.* »"
msgstr ""
"«*Les organitzacions de notícies també han de contribuir a aquest conjunt "
"d'eines de la comunitat. Hem de tenir [reporters] que aportin pedaços a PGP, "
"OTR i Tails. Aquestes organitzacions han de finançar millores de 5.000 o "
"10.000 dòlars per millorar aquestes eines. Perquè tothom confia en aquestes "
"eines i cap de les principals organitzacions que els beneficien realment "
"contribueix al seu desenvolupament.*»"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"Mediapart is the first news organization to officially endorse Tails and "
"answer our call for donations. We hope they are not going to be the last."
msgstr ""
"Mediapart és la primera organització de notícies que avala oficialment Tails "
"i respon a la nostra crida de donacions. Esperem que no siguin els últims."

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"If your organization is also interested in becoming a regular donor, please "
"contact us."
msgstr ""
"Si la vostra organització també està interessada a convertir-se en un donant "
"habitual, poseu-vos en contacte amb nosaltres."

